{"query_text":"
-- who are the top sellers of this C2C website ?
-- Which countries hold the best top sellers ? (i.e. Where should you go to get the best training ?)

-- Another study could try to answer the other way around (i.e. regarding BUYERA).
-- Example question:
-- Which countries hold the best buyers ? 
--   This answer would allow you to adapt your products to the style of the people from there

---------------------------------------------

-- Mininmum number of Products sold to be considered a top seller
DECLARE ?minProductsSold AS INTEGER = 20


SELECT
  country
column44: \n  \n  SUM(CASE gender WHEN \"F\" THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as femaleSellers
column45:
-- Stats for top sellers

  SUM(CASE WHEN productssold >= ?minProductsSold THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) nbTopSellers
column46: \n  SUM(CASE WHEN productssold >= ?minProductsSold THEN productssold ELSE 0 END) topTotalProductsSold
column47: \n  SUM(CASE WHEN productssold >= ?minProductsSold THEN productslisted ELSE 0 END) topTotalProductsListed
column48: \n  SUM(CASE WHEN productssold >= ?minProductsSold THEN socialnbfollowers ELSE 0 END) topFollowersCount
column49: \n  SUM(CASE WHEN productssold >= ?minProductsSold THEN socialnbfollows ELSE 0 END) topFollowingCount
column50: \n  SUM(CASE WHEN productssold >= ?minProductsSold THEN dayssincelastlogin ELSE 0 END) topTotalDaysSinceLastLogin
column51:
SUM(CASE WHEN (productssold >= ?minProductsSold AND gender = "F") THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) as topFemaleSellers

FROM `6m_0k_99k_users_dataset_public`
WHERE productssold > 0  -- filter to only successful sellers (not prospecting sellers)
-- around 130 sellers with >= 20 sold products
column52:
out of 98K users

GROUP BY country

--ORDER BY productssold DESC
--LIMIT 100;
) AS precomputedStats

WHERE (nbtopsellers > 0)
--ORDER BY totalproductssold DESC
--ORDER BY nbtopsellers DESC
ORDER BY topSellerRatio DESC

-- Tweet: """
-- Best fashion sellers come from these countries!
-- See this query and project to learn more.
-- #salespeople #sales #seller #bestseller #best
-- """"
